title: Twitter Limits Number of Posts Users Can Read
description: The social-media platform began limiting how many posts users can read, an unusual move that came as owner Elon Musk says he is fighting companies trying to use its data for developing artificial intelligence programs.

title: What Will AI Do to Your Job? Take a Look at What It's Already Doing to Coders
description: Artificial-intelligence software is eating the software industry, as companies turn to generative AI tools to save money on programmers. It’s a sign of what’s to come for many white-collar workers.
